criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Histological diagnosis of Renal Cell Carcinoma;

          2. Histological diagnosis of Carcinoma of the adrenal gland;

          3. Availability of histological material;

          4. For the evaluation of the prognostic role: no systemic treatment with TKI administered
             before surgery.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Unavailable histological material;

          2. For RCC: histological diagnosis different from Clear Cell histotype.
